
/*
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
###############################################################################
+ The AMC Squad
+ CON code by James Stanfield, Cedric "Sangman" Haegeman, Dino Bollinger,
+              Mikko Sandt, Cedric "Zaxtor" Lutes and Dan "Danarama" Gaskill
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* See AMC_MAIN.CON for a full list of script authors.

Feel free to use any code in the game for your own uses; just make
sure to mention the authors and/or "The AMC Squad" in your credits.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
NOTES:
This file contains the code for the bestiary instructions in the command interface

HOW TO SET UP:
1. Go to the appropriate mission info in CODE/GUI/COMM_MISS.CON
2. Scroll down to the state PRECOG_BOX section; the code in brackets after box toggle is the info needed
3. Underneath the main pic, you'll need to manually set a variable containing what enemies are in the map;
this involves checking the lists below, adding each value for what enemy type is present, than setting the
appropriate faction flag. So if the map has cycloids with pigcops and pig tanks, ps_cycloids would be set to 130.
you need to do this for each faction present, set their appropriate flags this way.
4. underneath this, add state precog_enemies
5. That should be it - double check the precog box in the mission interface.
6. TODO: some unique per-map enemies, bosses or special actors aren't included yet, will be done over time.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*/

var ei_x 95 0
var ei_y 35 0
var ei_icon 0 0

var ps_cycloids 0 0

// 1 = liztroops
// 2 = pigcops
// 4 = lizmen
// 8 = commander
// 16 = octabrain
// 32 = sentry drone
// 64 = battlelord
// 128 = pig tank
// 256 = protector drone
// 512 = Overlord
// 1024 = Cycloid Emporer
// 2048 = Alien Queen
// 4096 = High Emporer
// 8192 = Cyber Alien
// 16384 = Pig Riot shield
// 32768 = Elite Pigcop
